01:02:18.820 --> 01:02:20.948
- Officer.
- You're too late. I've seen it all.


946
01:02:21.030 --> 01:02:23.499
You have? I can explain everything.

947
01:02:23.575 --> 01:02:24.792
- You don't have to.
- I don't?


948
01:02:24.868 --> 01:02:26.962
Don't worry.
There's nothing illegal about any of this.


949
01:02:27.036 --> 01:02:28.083
Are you sure?

950
01:02:28.163 --> 01:02:29.790
Of course. This is America.

951
01:02:29.873 --> 01:02:32.717
- I see.
